    <item>
      <title>Aeriva: A Mini Autonomous Quadrotor Platform</title>
      <link>https://yichengchen.com/project/aeriva/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yichengchen.com/project/aeriva/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aeriva&lt;/strong&gt; - This name is a combination of &amp;ldquo;aero&amp;rdquo; (meaning air) and &amp;ldquo;diva&amp;rdquo; (suggesting a stylish and confident personality).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In March 2023, I began to design, assemble, and test this drone from scratch. So far, four drones of this type have been made and used in various scientific research and competitions in my lab.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agile and safe&lt;/strong&gt;: Aeriva is built upon a 3.5-inch cinewhoop frame with Kakute H7 mini flight controller, making it exceptionally agile, compact and safe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High computing performance&lt;/strong&gt;: Aeriva is equipped with NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX, facilitating it with strong onboard computing capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;specifications&#34;&gt;Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Component&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Specs&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Computer&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Camera&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Intel RealSense D435&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Stack&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Kakute H7 mini + Tekko32 F4 4in1 mini 45A ESC&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Dimension&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;152mm motor-to-motor&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Motors&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;RCinpower GTS V3 2104-T-1800kv&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Propellers&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Gemfan D90S&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Battery&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;6S 1200mah 150C&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;accomplishments-based-on-aeriva&#34;&gt;Accomplishments based on Aeriva&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Scientific research:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2309.10683&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Learning-Initialized Trajectory Planning in Unknown Environments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Competitions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../huashan_uav_challenge/&#34;&gt;Huashan UAV challenge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: I led a team of six students and won the championship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>2023 Huashan UAV Challenge - Champion</title>
      <link>https://yichengchen.com/project/huashan_uav_challenge/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yichengchen.com/project/huashan_uav_challenge/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Huashan UAV Challenge is a national competition for college students in China. The competition is held in the Huashan Mountain, Shaanxi Province. The 2023 Huashan UAV Challenge is the first time that the competition has been held. This competition requires two drones to bypass the threat area in the field and reach the target point simultaneously. The drones get their positions using UWB.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-role&#34;&gt;My Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I led a team of six students. I contirbuted to the system architecture of the drones, including the hardware and software. I provided a framework to achieve UWB positioning, communication between the drones and the ground station, trajectory planning, and tracking control based on ROS and PX4.&lt;/p&gt;
